    "is_free": true,
    "description": "Infinite Incantation is a charming papercraft-style bullet heaven action roguelike that will test your spell-slinging skills as you tear through waves of enemies. To survive against the horde, you'll have the chance to roll the dice to procedurally mutate your spells into powerful evolutions, allowing you to take on even tougher challenges. Customize your character with RPG-like upgrades and stack your deck with the spells you'll randomly draw in runs. With fast-paced action, challenging bosses, and endless spell-crafting possibilities, Infinite Incantation is a must-play for fans of spell-casting, screen-filling, and goblin slaying action.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/0e755cf49bf73e2a7feed8d5afb4830d.avif?t=1728558902\" width=616 height=104 /></span><br>Cast Shape Archetype + Element + Effect = <i>Infinite Incantations</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/a5c03b179b9100d8bd8c65fad045cdf5.poster.avif?t=1728558902\" width=616 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/a5c03b179b9100d8bd8c65fad045cdf5.webm?t=1728558902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/a5c03b179b9100d8bd8c65fad045cdf5.mp4?t=1728558902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Infinite Incantation uses a robust component spell system that can combine elements, casting styles, and special effects in a variety of different ways. Stryx, your (totally friendly and charming) owl companion can convert the experience points you collect into <strong>powerful spells</strong>. Like a spell?  Or even dislike it? Choose to randomly <strong>evolve it</strong> into something even stronger, whether through <strong>greater power</strong> or <strong>mutated attributes</strong>. The spell will randomly mutate into something even stronger and more wild. Who knows what kind of mayhem that'll ensue? There are <strong>hundreds of combinations</strong> you could need to adapt to on the fly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/db841bed39134daed708b792b857af2c.poster.avif?t=1728558902\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/db841bed39134daed708b792b857af2c.webm?t=1728558902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/db841bed39134daed708b792b857af2c.mp4?t=1728558902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/33bd60b326747875b763c63e9e236f65.avif?t=1728558902\" width=616 height=104 /></span><br>You can customize the type of mage you want to be and how you want to interact with the deep component spell system.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/051b3eecfced2ddf1e18c150a17a6ef7.poster.avif?t=1728558902\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/051b3eecfced2ddf1e18c150a17a6ef7.webm?t=1728558902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/051b3eecfced2ddf1e18c150a17a6ef7.mp4?t=1728558902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Level up and upgrade your stats.<br></li><li>Specialize in certain elemental affinities.<br></li><li>Build your deck of spell archetype cards before heading out.<br></li><li>Mutate spells on the fly and roll the dice to see what you get.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/66405b2262f78c114d11cdbd03397c57.avif?t=1728558902\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/c296a97b383b92a35cba8fb8c7ce78f0.avif?t=1728558902\" width=616 height=104 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tear up seemingly endless hordes of monsters and bosses all vying for your demise.<br></li><li>Twin-Stick Shooter-type controls.<br></li><li>Cast spells manually or automatically.<br></li><li>Play with a controller or a keyboard and mouse.<br></li><li>No scissors or glue required.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/38a3ca2b846144cc302bef1be2f1a860.poster.avif?t=1728558902\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/38a3ca2b846144cc302bef1be2f1a860.webm?t=1728558902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286260/extras/38a3ca2b846144cc302bef1be2f1a860.mp4?t=1728558902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
